author: COMSOL
description: This example demonstrates the mixing of fluids using laminar layered flow in a MEMS mixer. The mixer has several lamellae of microchannels, and the two fluids to be mixed are alternated for every second layer. The fluid travels in the channels from back to front by pressure-driven flow.
label: lamella_mixer.mph
